description:
Get the song here: http://smarturl.it/take-back-the-night
This is part 2 of a 4 part series, go watch the others!
1. Fallen Kingdom: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I-sH53vXP2A&list=PL1C4ECC7E38737799&index=3
3. Find the Pieces: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lyu7-Jcyl_8&list=PL1C4ECC7E38737799&index=5
4. Dragonhearted: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=07rtl-zcQhg&list=PL1C4ECC7E38737799&index=6

Songs playlist ► https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2rDbRUDkds&list=PL1C4ECC7E38737799
Behind the scenes: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PIvzmrOZpXg

Credits:
Modeling, rigging, animation, post production, and effects by Bootstrap Buckaroo
http://www.youtube.com/user/DigBuildLive
Animation by Slamacow Creations:
http://www.youtube.com/user/SlamacowCreations
Animated, directed, and produced by CaptainSparklez:
http://www.youtube.com/user/CaptainSparklez
Take Back the Night written and performed by TryHardNinja:
http://www.youtube.com/user/TryHardNinja
Audio production by Doc Exx:
http://www.youtube.com/user/DocExxMusic
Vocal production and editing by The Jerry Farley:
http://www.youtube.com/thejerryfarley
Sets by FyreUK:
https://www.youtube.com/user/FyreUK

Lyrics:
Closet full of secrets and skeletons awakes but nothing's true
I used to own a castle now it's boxes that I have to move 
Right here in the darkness there's nothing left for me to do
It's easier to run away but today
Today we got to

Cast the shadows out from sight
A final stand a shouting cry
All the wrongs now turned to right
So fight the past 
Take back the night
And call upon the torch tonight
To bring out all the ghosts to light 
Because at last we have to go it's time
To take back the night

Bridges burned and broken on different sides we start anew
Being chased by monsters to face head on or be consumed
Reaching out for something grasping on to nothing to lose
Paybacks left too long unpaid but today
Today we got to

Cast the shadows out from sight
A final stand a shouting cry
All the wrongs now turned to right
So fight the past 
Take back the night
And call upon the torch tonight
To bring out all the ghosts to light 
Because at last we have to go it's time
To take back the night
